Class Style.colors

java.lang.Object
Style.colors
Enclosing class:
Style
public static class Style.colors extends Object
Provides ANSI color codes for styling console output. This class contains constants representing various background and text colors using ANSI escape codes. The colors are defined for aesthetic purposes, such as representing a chessboard theme or providing highlights.
